      "description": "Looking for an affordable project to make your own? This vehicle is the ultimate mechanic\u2019s special! While it definitely needs a significant amount of work and some serious TLC to get back on the road, it\u2019s a fantastic opportunity for someone who loves to tinker and restore cars. If you\u2019re ready to roll up your sleeves, this is a budget-friendly way to start your next automotive adventure!",
