    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is for parts or as a major project. The exterior has extensive rust along the wheel wells and several large dents on the passenger side. Mechanically, the engine starts but runs roughly, and the transmission requires immediate attention as it struggles to engage higher gears. Inside, the cabin shows significant wear with torn seating and a broken dashboard. This car is not currently roadworthy and will need to be towed. It is best suited for someone looking for a donor vehicle or a complete restoration project.",
