      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a pristine example of automotive excellence, maintained to a showroom standard that truly defies its age. The exterior boasts a mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, scratches, or swirl marks, having been meticulously detailed and protected by a high-end ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather seats show no signs of wear, and the original factory scent still lingers. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, functions flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified specialists using OEM parts. With exceptionally low mileage and a complete service history provided, this car offers a driving experience indistinguishable from a new vehicle. It has been garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen inclement weather. For the discerning collector or enthusiast seeking a truly flawless specimen, this is an unrivaled opportunity.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
